@Node AFFICON "STCCG.guide/Glossary/affiliation icon"
@TOC MAIN
@INDEX INDEX

  @{b}affiliation icon@{ub}

A round icon in the upper left corner of a Personnel
or Ship card or lower left corner of a Facility card, indicating the
card's affiliation or its Non-Aligned or Neutral status. Also, a
rectangular icon on a Mission card indicating which affiliations (or
Non-Aligned) can attempt the mission.(Although Non-Aligned and Neutral
are not affiliations, the icons are still called affiliation icons.)

@Endnode

@Node AIRLOCK "STCCG.guide/Glossary/Airlock"
@TOC MAIN
@INDEX INDEX

  @{b}Airlock@{ub}

