@INDEX INDEX

  @{b}Bajoran Wormhole@{ub}

The Alpha Quadrant Bajoran Wormhole card must be placed or inserted
adjacent to a Bajor Region location if any are on the spaceline. If
not, the doorway may be inserted anywhere on the spaceline that is
not within another region, creating a Bajor Region. If one end of
the Bajoran Wormhole is destroyed, the other end is discarded also.
See @{"doorways - closed" link "XXPATH:glossary.guide/DOORCLOSED"}.

Moving through this pair of doorways can be part of a single movement
action to the mouth of the Bajoran Wormhole and through it (continuing
along the spaceline upon exit if Wormhole Navigation Schematic is
played).

@Endnode

